data.description: Discover the potential in this spacious 3-bedroom home boasting a well-designed layout. Nestled on a serene street, it features a ready-to-be-finished full basement, providing ample space for additional living and bedrooms. The mudroom grants access to a 2-car garage and a covered patio overlooking the large fenced-in yard, complete with a storage shed and fire pit area. Recent upgrades include new A/C and luxurious LVP flooring in the kitchen/dining. Abundant natural light floods in through the windows, enhancing the charm of the hardwood floors. Unleash your creativity and build equity by modernizing the kitchen and bathroom or completing the basement. A promising opportunity awaits.
